item.title: Tiny11 On a Dell Latitude E4510
item.description: So I had this old Dell E5410 that was just sitting on a shelf collecting dust. And I had just discovered a modified version of Win11 called Tiny11. So it only seemed natural for me to try and install one on the other. But first of all, the specs: Laptop Specifications Processor: Intel Core i5-450M Memory: 8GB DDR3L 1600 CL11 RAM Storage: 128GB SSD Wireless: Intel Centrino Advanced-N 6235 So with that out of the way let’s get into the installation: I had no issues.
